Google.OrTools.Sat.CpSolverStatus
CpSolverStatus
The status returned by a solver trying to solve a CpModelProto.
Definition: CpModel.pb.cs:204
Google.OrTools.Sat.CpSolverStatus.Infeasible
@ Infeasible
The problem has been proven infeasible.
Google.OrTools.Sat.CpSolverStatus.Unknown
@ Unknown
The status of the model is still unknown.
Google.OrTools.Sat.CpSolverStatus.Feasible
@ Feasible
A feasible solution has been found.
Google.OrTools.Sat.CpSolverStatus.ModelInvalid
@ ModelInvalid
The given CpModelProto didn't pass the validation step.
Google.OrTools.Sat.CpSolverStatus.Optimal
@ Optimal
An optimal feasible solution has been found.
